<div xmlns:perseus="http://www.perseus.org/meta/perseus.rdfs#" xmlns:dctype="http://purl.org/dc/dcmitype/" xmlns:tufts="http://www.tufts.edu/" xmlns:alph="http://alpheios.net/namespaces/tei" class="alpheios-lex-text_container en">
    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n3084" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἔμ-πεδος</span></b>  (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πέδον</span>): <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">firmly standing</span> or
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">footed</span>, <i><span class="en">Od. 23.203</span></i>,
            <i><span class="en">Il. 13.512</span></i>; <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">firm, immovable,
            unshaken</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 12.9</span></i>, 12; so of
          the mind, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">βίη, μένος, φρένες</span>,
          ‘unimpaired,’ <i><span class="en">Od. 10.493</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">; ἔμπεδος οὐδ᾽ ἀεσίφρων</span> (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">Πρίαμος</span>), <i><span class="en">Il.
            20.183</span></i>; ‘sure,’ ‘certain,’ <i><span class="en">Od.
            19.250</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Od. 8.30</span></i>; of time,
          ‘lasting,’ ‘constant,’ <i><span class="en">Il. 8.521</span></i>,
            <i><span class="en">Od. 8.453</span></i>; and metaph., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἦτορ, φρένες, Ζ 352</span>, <i><span class="en">Od. 18.215</span></i>.—Neut. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἔμπεδον</span> as adv., with the same meanings, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">στηρίξαι</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">firmly</span>, <i><span class="en">Od. 12.434</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">; μένειν</span>, without leaving the spot,
            <i><span class="en">Il. 5.527</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">; θέειν</span>, ‘constantly,’ <i><span class="en">Il. 13.141</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Od.
            13.86</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
